<br>
<br>
<br>
In the Mists of a Mountain all shouded in cloud,<br>
Stands a Temple of Gold, where no voice is raised loud,<br>
In the milk of honey'd ambrosia, the heart sets a pace;<br>
This Island of Gods,  where they rule from this place.<br>
<br>
Here is Olympus, Olympia devine<br>
Here is a place, I once dreamed be mine;<br>
Here in marble where Noble gods walked<br>
Here, is a place where I once sat and talked.<br>
<br>
This is a place of legend and Myth<br>
Rising up like a great morning mist,<br>
A mist which unlike fog of the mind<br>
Brought clarity and purpose to a people of kind.<br>
<br>
This is the place where noble Gods roam,<br>
This is the place where my story be told<br>
For here once I served Lord Zeus and Hera<br>
Here is the place, where born the bright star.<br>
<br>
Oh Olympus, great hill of a thousand great tales,<br>
Of Olympian's in majesty, not meekly nor frail,<br>
Wherein sat the gods, where my story begins<br>
This is the place wherein the gods live.<br>
<br>
Oh Great Olympus, how long they forgot<br>
Your life, your history has not been for nought<br>
For Legacy make and legacy leave<br>
Great civilisatins to thy to thy towers still cleave<br>
<br>
And this is my tale, my heart sings it out<br>
This is the Temple wherein Gods be about<br>
This is the Mount which inspires devine,<br>
This is the place wherein true light shine.<br>
<br>
A Light which brought hope to those who believed<br>
A storm calming light, all fears relieved;<br>
This is the place where our journey did start<br>
This is the core and the soul of our hearts<br>
<br>
<br>
Goddess Bia (Tiya)  2002 <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showPrevMessage?topicID=273.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showNextMessage?topicID=273.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=273.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/blueMoon/addReply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.emailToFriend?topicID=273.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.threadControl?topicID=273.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/blueMoon/deleteThread.jpg border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=273.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=273.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub11.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="amazonsuniteamazonsunitescrollboard">Amazons Unite Scroll Board<option value="amazonsunitefrm39">Guild Applications<option value="amazonsunitefrm37">The Mythical Odyssey Forum<option value="amazonsunitefrm23">The Olympian Gods<option value="amazonsunitefrm15">Black Sea Tavern and